      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's an interesting way to put it. but isn't there a danger there? if every group gets an exemption just because they claim it conflicts with their beliefs, doesn't that eventually make the law meaningless? like, how do you stop it from just becoming a way for people to ignore any law they don't like?",
